<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咚……咚……咚……唧！唧！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西靠超级听力听到很多学校里寻常的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她听到画室里面水槽滴水的声音，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>以及幼儿园教室里面蟋蟀鸣叫的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是她也听到了一个不寻常的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个低沉的嗓音从学校地下传来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“干活儿！干活儿！干活儿！”有人咆哮着，“快点儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是思维普斯的声音！”罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我就知道不能够信任他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞快地跑到了地下室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她来到一扇被锁的大门前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西紧紧地盯着这扇门，激光从她的眼睛里面射出。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞轰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大门被炸开了，罗西马上冲了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地下室是空着的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西瞅了瞅四周，发现一个地板门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跑了过去，打开了地板门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跳了下去，落在了一个大洞穴里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在那里，罗西看到所有的学生们都在做苦工。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一些在用铁锹凿石头墙，一些在推着小推车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这难道是一个矿井？”罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看四周，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>发现一个学生正在从墙里面拉出一块闪闪发光的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”罗西深吸了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一个钻石矿井！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的学生都带着思维普斯给的星星胸针。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有人看到火箭女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都在忙着干活儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这真是太奇怪了。”罗西自言自语道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到了特勒尔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里发生什么了？”罗西朝他喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是特勒尔并没有回答，他甚至都没有看她一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他被催眠了！”罗西恍然大悟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家都被催眠了！这都是因为那些星星胸针。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然间，杰克和玛拉从后面抓住了罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她本来想用力挣脱他们，但是马上觉得这并不是什么好主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她不想伤害她的朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>思维普斯出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你以为可以阻止我，是吧？”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西发现他的手上戴着一个闪闪发亮的星星戒指。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里发生了什么？”罗西质问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们学校的地下有很多的钻石。”思维普斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想拥有它们！我催眠了所有的老师，让他们离开小镇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>之后我又催眠了你的同学们，让他们为我挖钻石。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>思维普斯咯咯一笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要变成富翁了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你逃不掉的！”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>思维普斯笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，那可不一定！”他看了杰克和玛拉一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把这个犯人带过来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>